<br>
Prayer Shawl + Treeweave beats Obulus Shroud + SoN in my book, you're trading trading 1 wis, and 8FR/CR away for 7 AC.  I swap a Tattered Mantle (12 ac, some hps) and the Prayer Shawl, depending on the situation.  <br>
<br>
I'm currently looking for Coldain Skin Gloves, a Chetari Shield for a cloak, and a Sarnak Battle Shield.  They're all a tad beyond my budget, but obtainable with the right groups.  You could fight at the Chardok zone for a while and get a shot at a shield in a couple days.<br>
<br>
